productReviews.reviewText: It only works when I'm Finland.
one of my hobbies is skateboarding. and when i'm skateboarding this works great.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
I tried to annihilate it but got bonbon all over it.
My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
